quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  11,46,"Alla daalani Nuuhu: Ko an yo Nuuhu, pellet …ìi…ó…óo maa mo tori-…óaa Lam da…óndugol on, o jeyaaka e …ìeynguure maa nde Mi fodu maa nden; tawde ko o keefeero. Pellet ndee toraare maa yo Nuuhu, ko gollal ngal mo∆¥∆¥ah, ngal yaadah e jogitii…óo martaba maa…óa. Wata a toro Lam ko a alanaa …óum ganndal. Min Mi…óo rentina maa nde jeyete-…óaa e majju…ìe …ìen, haa toro-…óaa Lam ko lunndii ganndal Am e hikma Am."
  11,47,"Annabi Nuuhu maaki: Joomi am, mi…óo moolora Maa, da…óndinora Maa nde mi lanndoto Maa ko mi alanaa …óum ganndal. Si wanah A hafranam goopol am ngol, yurme-∆äaa mi yurmeende Maa nden, mi jeyete e …ìen hayru…ìe laakara."
  11,48,"Alla daalani Nuuhu (yo o his): Ko an yo Nuuhu, jippor e laana kan ka leydi wonndude e kisal e hoolaare, e neemaaji …óuu…óu…ói hoore-maa…óa immorde ka Alla -e hoore jurriiyaaji …ìen gom…óim…ìe wonndunoo…ìe e maa…óa ka laana aroyoo…ìe …ìaawo maa…óa. Mofte goo e …ìi…ó…ìe ma…ì…ìe yeddu…ìe …ìen, aray Men dakmita …ìe e …óam nguurndam aduna, Men newinana …ìe ko …ìe wuurira; refti memoya …ìe ka laakara immorde e Amen, lepte muusu…óe."
  11,49,"Qissa Nuuhu on ko jeyaa…óo e kumpite wirnii…óe. An Nulaa…óo, a anndaano …óe an, yim…ìe maa …ìen kadi anndaano …óe ado oo wahayu mo Men wahayini e maa…óa. Mu√±√±or lorra yim…ìe maa …ìen e ko …ìe fennata kon, wano Annabi Nuuhu mu√±√±ornoo. Pellet ballal ngal e poolal ngal, wonanii …óoftotoo…ìe yamirooje Alla …óen …ìe wo…ó…óitoo ha…óaa…ói Makko …óin."
  11,50,"Men Nuli kadi faade e Aadinkoo…ìe …ìen, musi…ó…óo ma…ì…ìe on Huudi (yo o his). O maakani …ìe: Ko onon yo yim…ìe, rewee Alla tun, wata on kafidu Mo e gooto. Rewetee…óo e goonga alanah on ko woori Mo. On wonaali e ngol nodditagol mon wonnde himo mari kafidii…óo, si wanaa ko on fenoo…ìe."
  11,51,"Ko onon yo yim…ìe am, mi …óa…ì…ìiraa on njo…ìdi e ko mi yottinta e mon kon, mi noddira on …óum immorde ka Joomi am. Njo…ìdi am wonaali si wanah ka Alla tagu…óo lam on. E on haqqiltah …óum? Nooto…óon noddaandu am ndun?"
  11,52,"Ko onon yo yim…ìe am, …óa…ì…ìiree Alla haforanal, refti tuubanon Mo junuubi mon …óin, …ìuri mawnude e majji ko sirku. O yo…ìitiray on …óum jippingol to…ìo …óuu…óungo, O …ìeyda on teddungal e hoore teddungal mon ngal …óuu…óireede …ìi…ó…ìe e jawle. Wata on …óuurno e ko mi noddata on kon, laatoron ngol …óuurngal mon …óon bom…ìe e yeddu…ìe Alla fennu…ìe ko mi addi kon."
  11,53,"Yim…ìe makko …ìen wi'i: "Ko an yo Huudu, a adda-ranaali men hujja …ìanngu…óo fii no men gom…óinire. Men wonaali kadi accitiroo…ìe rewetee…ói amen …óin fii konngol maa ko aldah hujja. Men wonaali gom…ói- noo…ìe ma e kon ko noddataa e mun wonnde ko a Nulaa…óo."